irectly to Ayush", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "March 28, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "I feel very lucky to work with Ayush, who is a great manager with such high level of task-oriented. He is indeed one of rare persons possessed strong interpersonal skills in motivating others. As a team player, he always shows extensive listening skills and unrivaled sense of responsibility. And I strongly believe in his future success no matter where he goes.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Hong N", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Marketing & Analytics Professional", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nhunghnguyen2012/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAex8a8BX_1W71U7Fryf7VA79TT6pDC6EKE", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "July 6, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I was in the same batch as Ayush at I.H.M, Bangalore and in fact in the same group too. He is a hand working and sincere person and does his work with dedication. Ayush likes to learn new skills and acquire new knowledge. He has great potential. Its been a pleasure knowing and working with him in class. I wish him all the best for his future.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Atyasha Singh", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Head of Consultancy Services at Impactt, India | Responsible Sourcing & Human Rights | Supply Chain Due Diligence | Social Impact | HRDD", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/atyashasingh/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAGcKtMBPRnReeHQOA_F_j4oz1TRosfpbuw", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Rizwan Ahmad Siddiqui worked with Ayush on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "June 5, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "“Ayush is a cheerful person and a task oriented manager who manages his work and his team efficiently. Professionally he is focused, good team leader and proactive. I have always found him to be 