with Jeet during our time together at Conrad Koh Samui, where he served as Director of Finance. Jeet is an exceptional financial leader, whose expertise and strategic vision significantly contributed to the success and financial stability of the property.\n\nWhat sets Jeet apart is his strong analytical mind combined with an ability to communicate complex financial insights in a clear and actionable way. His proactive approach to problem-solving and his deep understanding of financial operations made him an invaluable partner in decision-making and strategic planning.\n\nJeet is not only a highly skilled finance professional but also a true team player. He fosters collaboration across departments, creating an environment where financial goals align seamlessly with the overall objectives of the business. His leadership, integrity, and attention to detail are qualities that any organization would be lucky to have.\n\nIt was a pleasure working alongside Jeet, and I would highly recommend him for any senior finance leadership role.", "recommendations/0/name": "Jitendra Chawla", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Director of Finance @ Hilton | Financial Management Expert", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jitendra-chawla-95565618/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAOnytEB6iZ5W7LgIh1VoZhISeuaMBWse74", "recommendations/1/context": "Marco was senior to Begona but didn't manage Begona directly", "recommendations/1/date": "September 5, 2024", "recommendations/1/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Begona during my time at Waldorf Astoria Maldives, where she served as Director of HR. Begona is an exceptional HR leader with a deep understanding of human resources and a remarkable ability to build strong teams. Her strategic thinking and commitment to employee well-being were key drivers in fostering a positive and high-performing work culture.\n\nBegona consistently went above and beyond to ensure that both staff and leadership felt supported, creating an environment where collaboration and growth thrived. Her leadership style is inclusive, approachable, and highly effective—always maintaining a balance between achieving organizational goals and prioritizing the development of her team.\n\nShe has a natural ability to navigate complex situations with professionalism and grace, making her an invaluable asset to any organization. I am grateful for the opportunity to have worked alongside her and highly recommend her for any leadership position in HR.", "recommendations/1/name": "Begona Campoy", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Cluster Human Resources Director", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/begona-campoy-56b52210/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAI2bqMBK7OSUvZSIGADU1m-pb2Kp-B0FW8", "recommendations/2/date": "February 3, 2022", "recommendations/2/description": "\nI have worked with Sophie during my internship period at Paiza. \nSophie is a very talented leader that drives the team towards continuous improvement and training. Sophie has a great attention to detail and displays a visible management style towards developing talent that makes Sophie a mentor to many employees. ", "recommendations/2/name": "Sophie Chen, ICF ACC", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "I provoke passionate and ambitious female leaders in hospitality to articulate their strengths and amplify their voices though coaching", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sophiechencoach/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABmDU4MB0ol5cRpOjtb4kauuGuvIpsPDEss", "recommendations/3/context": "Marco worked with Saudi on the same team", "recommendations/3/date": "February 19, 2020", "recommendations/3/description": "I rarely come across to a real Human Resources talent who stand out like Saudi. I had the pleasure of working with Saudi for over two years at Conrad Koh Samui and collaborating on daily basis. Saudi’s ability to handle multiple tasks or issues that arises was great and made a big difference for our resort in particular to operation. No matter how tense the situation, Saudi made sure that everyone was kept on the right path and always with a smile. As DHR, team member and colleague, Saudi earns my highest recommendation.", "recommendations/3/name": "Saudi Khaneng", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Country Lead, HR - Thailand & The Maldives @ IHG Hotels & Resorts | Driving all strategic HR dimensions realistically and practically.", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/saudikhaneng/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAqKzSQB8kLpaSo_6d8giCm-vW2pxJrBQBU", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "November 26, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Marco is a very talented and energetic hotel operation leader. He maintains great relationships with all staffs from down to top. He brings energy to everyone in the leadership team. He is a hands-on leader who will be around with his team members to ensure that the team has his support. He has great customer management skill/knowledge and has displayed excellent focus in guest satisfaction. Marco has great potential in hotel industry especially in luxury sector of hospitality. I trust that he will be an great asset to any organization that he works for.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Saudi Khaneng", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Country Lead, HR - Thailand & The Maldives @ IHG Hotels & Resorts | Driving all strategic HR dimensions realistically and practically.", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/saudikhaneng/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAqKzSQB8kLpaSo_6d8giCm-vW2pxJrBQBU", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Cherrie reported directly to Marco", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "April 19, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "A driven and team orientated talent. A true leader to work with. ", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Cherrie Iek", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Luxury Retail | Client Experience | Retail Marketing", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/cherrie-iek-57b75779/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABCpq28BlLDwqt8sEOvdi2yS8QzT9x9vlks", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "José worked with Marco on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "March 17, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Marco is a diligent and dedicated professional. He is now conducting process improvements using Kaizen concepts, value stream mapping and practical problem solving. His determination make him an asset to the team of in-house kaizen facilitators we have.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "José Ferreira Pinto", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Arithmocracy: in coming!", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/joseferreirapinto/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABABiEBLCqPc82ODrJLhXDTliPBbApbhYM", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Joana worked with Marco but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "February 3, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Marco is highly motivated, dedicated and energetic, always aiming to improve processes and the service level at his work place. I firmly believe that Marco's know-how and strong-will can add value to any hospitality industry related company.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Joana M.", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Lean Management", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/joana-m-9b867445/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAmH75wBQL9IJG4RgyGpgnQX6pWLTjbpmeU", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Eliana worked with Marco but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "January 13, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "I've work with Marco while he was part of the ESHTE's Student's Academic Association, . \nHe has proven to be a hard worker, attentive to detail, never losing his mind even when under stress, with a very professional attitude towards all the clients. \nI wouldn't hesitate in hire him or recomending him to a position on Bar Management.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Eliana Sousa", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "MNE", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/eliana-sousa-94a82018/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAOuR0oBs8EcVprka3rp0vTAUM0ZCyC4E4s", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Adriana worked with Marco on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "September 19, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "Marco would be a valuable addition to any company he chooses to join, I highly recommend him for any position. Marco knows how to get the job done quickly and effectively, he also works great as a part of a team and can act as a leader when required.", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Adriana Venegas", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "Directora Digital en Interaction.cr", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/adrianavenegas/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAoXilYBZ9DiuGUKWWGKqNluKDXXdIEKXx4", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Charles was senior to Marco but didn't manage Marco directly", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "February 22, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Marco at Paiza at Venetian Macao Resort Hotel. I was the Director Of Paiza Operations and Marco was the F&B Supervisor at Paiza Dining.\n\nMarco has a very professional approach towards his job in that he executes his reaponsibilities efficiently and the ability to blend with an environment that has predominantly chinese speaking staff and VIP gamers from Mainland China. \n\nMarco has a keen eye for detail and displays a visible management style in the operations which makes him effective supervisor. He has the ability to take on a bigger role in his area of expertise and I have no hesitation in giving my highest recommendation to any prospective employer.", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Charles Ratnasingam", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "Director Of Paiza Venetian Hotel Operations", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/charles-ratnasingam-3281b224/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAUDFlABJiaxDomIkLop9puRLdE2s3-3cD8", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Sara worked with Marco on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "November 5, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "Marco is a perfect example of professionalism in the hospitality business. He is courteous, humorous and very  helpful to his guests, as-well as he is with his teammates. He his always trying to figure out ways to better satisfy everyone in his work environment, whether they will be his  peers, superiors or customers. This is what makes him perfect to have around.", "recommendationsReceived/7/name": "Sara Outeiro", "recommendationsReceived/7/subtitle": "Head of Business Development @ Optimize Investment Partners | EU Residency by Investment | Investment Funds | Golden Visa | Investment Migration", "recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/saraouteiro/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWrvCsBSBZ9DkvGDH3O9A_U43de6nv5cms", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Marco was senior to lorenzo but didn't manage lorenzo directly", "recommendationsReceived/8/date": "July 6, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/8/description": "Marco is a good supervisor.,well respected ..,a  funny and cool guy as well..,have an eye on his colleagues..,and a very positive/optimistic person..", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "lorenzo bonsay", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "Captain at Venetian Resort Hotel Macao (Paiza)", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/lorenzo-bonsay-09626554/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAttoDIBfpr9kdFIAunD-E3SZnEtYnMfyvE", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "Maria Carmelita worked with Marco on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "July 2, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/9/description": "Mr. Marco is a detailed oriented supervisor who is attentive in all aspects.A good partner in my Team. Always there to give a helping hand.\nReally enjoying working with him.A very funny and cool guy as well.\nKeep it up, you'll go far.", "recommendationsReceived/9/name": "Maria Carmelita Escudal Faustino Martins", "recommendationsReceived/9/subtitle": "Paiza F&B Gaming - Manager II at The Venetian® Macao-Resort-Hotel Founder of MCM Chilli Garlic Oil", "recommendationsReceived/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/maria-carmelita-escudal-faustino-martins-3929b653/", "recommendationsReceived/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAtcQZ4Bdfex6r22ktlmEM2gvr_Fo9iK55s", "recommendationsReceived/10/context": "Nuno managed Marco directly", "recommendationsReceived/10/date": "January 15, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/10/description": "Durante o período Marco  manteve conduta pessoal e profissional irrepreensíveis, motivo pelo qual recomendo seus serviços, nada havendo que o desabone.", "recommendationsReceived/10/name": "Nuno Martins", "recommendationsReceived/10/subtitle": "Chefe de Cozinha", "recommendationsReceived/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nuno-martins-a9248826/", "recommendationsReceived/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAVo1A4B_3Au1T-vuowRwMhdd_wbhNWlc4o", "recommendationsReceived/11/context": "João worked with Marco on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/11/date": "January 9, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/11/description": "I had the opportunity to study at ESHTE and work with Mr. Marco Araujo in two different occasions, at the Arts Barcelona and at Gran Bahia Principe Rivera Maya.\nMarco always have been behaving like responsible, honest, proactive and hard working. During the time I worked with him, he willingly took on extra responsibilities when required and carried out all duties to high standards.\nI wish Marco every success for his future career and know that he will be a great leader to any company he joins.", "recommendationsReceived/11/name": "João Jeremias", "recommendationsReceived/11/subtitle": "General Manager | Distinctive Hospitality | Driving Operational Excellence", "recommendationsReceived/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/joaojeremias/", "recommendationsReceived/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALK1j4BgMmbJORv0h_f4mFtCy5_xKMYPVc", "recommendationsReceived/12/date": "January 3, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/12/description": "Marco Araujo has proven to be a very responsible student, and an active member of ESHTE's community. \nHe has allways been very suportive of all his collegues, a very consciencious staff member in every event he was involved, and a leader as the vice president of the student's association. \nI believe he'll be a excellent staff member in every company that choses to give him the opportunity to developed his skills.", "recommendationsReceived/12/name": "Eliana Sousa", "recommendationsReceived/12/subtitle": "MNE", "recommendationsReceived/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/eliana-sousa-94a82018/", "recommendationsReceived/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAOuR0oBs8EcVprka3rp0vTAUM0ZCyC4E4s", "recommendationsReceived/13/date": "January 3, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/13/description": "Marco is a person with a very strong personality, full of vigor! It is motivating to work with him, because for him nothing is impossible.\nHis education and good disposition make him known to perform very well in different situations! It was with great pleasure that I worked with him at the students Association, Estoril Higher Institute for Tourism and Hotel Studies, where I had the opportunity to come across your great character. And so i recommend him for sure!", "recommendationsReceive