('Simone Delle Foglie', 'Simone', 'Delle Foglie', 'Italian Culinary Specialist | Master Pizza Chef & Dough Expert | Luxury Hospitality & F&B Operations', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/simonegothailand', 'simonegothailand', $${"about": "25 years of mastery, from the heat of the oven to the heart of the Thai jungle.\n\nMy career is defined by two constants: precision and passion. With over two decades of deep-rooted expertise in Italian culinary arts—specializing in the high-level craft of authentic Pizza—I have built a reputation for excellence that transitions seamlessly from the kitchen to international tourism consultancy.\n\nThe Culinary Edge\n\nWith 25+ years of hands-on experience, I don’t just cook; I engineer flavors. My \"super-competence\" in pizza and Italian gastronomy isn't just about recipes—it’s about the science of fermentation, the sourcing of prime ingredients, and the management of high-pressure environments. I help brands and businesses translate the soul of Italian food into world-class dining experiences.\n\nThe Destination Specialist\n\nSince 2006, I have been a leading Destination Management Consultant (DMC) for Thailand. By bridging my roots in Puglia with my extensive network in Southeast Asia through \"VIVI LA THAILANDIA TRAVEL,\" I design travel experiences that are culturally immersive, logistically flawless, and adventurous by nature.\n\nThe Ultra-Endurance Mindset\n\nWhether I am scaling a mountain, finishing a marathon, or launching a new project, I apply the same \"Ultra\" discipline. I thrive on pushing boundaries and conquering the unknown.\n\nCore Competencies:\n\nCulinary: Master Pizza Consultant, Italian Gastronomy, Kitchen Management, Menu Engineering.\n\nTourism: Thailand DMC Specialist, Cultural Mediation, Luxury & Adventure Itinerary Design.\n\nPersonal: Professional Photography, Ultra-Sports, Cross-Cultural Leadership.\n\nLet’s Connect. Whether you are looking for culinary consultancy, Thai market entry, or simply a fellow adventurer to share insights with—I am ready for the next challenge.", "addressCountryOnly": "Thailand", "addressWithCountry": "Bangkok Metropolitan Area, Thailand", "addressWithoutCountry": "Bangkok Metropolitan Area", "backgroundPic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D16AQFI00P7ZrCB8g/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/B4DZzBqNYYG0AY-/0/1772775598589?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=31E50To5YpbDttVW9COv_iu6uCTEP93HOnkiN1kEVcE", "companyLinkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/apuliabangkok/", "companyName": "Apulia Bangkok", "connections": "6", "creatorWebsite/0/category": "COMPANY", "creatorWebsite/0/url": "https://www.instagram.com/apuliabangkok", "currentJobDuration": "9 mos", "currentJobDurationInYrs": "0.75", "experiences/0/companyId": "109232625", "experiences/0/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/apuliabangkok/", "experiences/0/companyName": "Apulia Bangkok", "experiences/0/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:109232625", "experiences/0/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/0/jobLocation": "Bangkok, Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/0/jobStartedOn": "8-2025", "experiences/0/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/0/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQE-BG1VMtqkAg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZn4Ez1iGYAY-/0/1760803635740?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=NCC39T1J9biu8knIyK_u-NApDGRMOL4RmMq2RXfVmug", "experiences/0/title": "Co-Founder and Pizza Chef", "experiences/1/companyName": "Vivi la Thailandia Travel", "experiences/1/employmentType": "Contract", "experiences/1/jobDescription": "Vivi la Thailandia Travel: Your Bridge Between Puglia and Thailand\n\nVivi la Thailandia Travel is the premier DMC (Destination Management Consultant) and Tour Operator specializing exclusively in Thailand, with a strategic operational base in Puglia, Italy.\n\nSince 2006, we have transformed a passion for adventure into a high-end travel consultancy. Our mission is to bridge the gap between Italian excellence and Thai authenticity, delivering unforgettable journeys that go far beyond the standard tourist trail.\n\nWhy Partner With Us?\n\nDual-Base Advantage: With deep roots in Thailand and a physical presence in Puglia, we offer Italian clients direct, face-to-face consultancy and seamless on-site management.\n\nHyper-Local Expertise: We don't just book trips; we curate experiences. Our extensive local network of guides, artisans, and restaurateurs ensures access to the \"unseen\" Thailand.\n\nBespoke Design: From pristine archipelagos to lush mountain treks, every itinerary is custom-engineered to match the specific desires of the modern traveler.\n\nEnd-to-End Support: We provide 360° assistance—from the first sketch of an itinerary to 24/7 ground support—ensuring total safety, comfort, and peace of mind.\n\nExperience the true essence of Thailand with the reliability of an Italian partner.", "experiences/1/jobLocation": "Bangkok", "experiences/1/jobStartedOn": "4-2024", "experiences/1/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/1/title": "Destination Manager", "experiences/2/companyName": "The Factory Rawai", "experiences/2/employmentType": "Contract", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "7-2025", "experiences/2/jobLocation": "Phuket, Thailand", "experiences/2/jobStartedOn": "3-2025", "experiences/2/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/2/title": "Head Pizza Chef", "experiences/3/companyId": "2761237", "experiences/3/companyIndustry": "Sporting Goods Manufacturing", "experiences/3/companyName": "Decathlon UK", "experiences/3/companySize": "1001-5000", "experiences/3/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:2761237", "experiences/3/companyWebsite": "https://www.decathlon.co.uk/", "experiences/3/jobEndedOn": "2-2024", "experiences/3/jobLocationCountry": "GB", "experiences/3/jobStartedOn": "9-2023", "experiences/3/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/3/title": "Sports Specialist", "experiences/4/companyId": "20095273", "experiences/4/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/4/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/